{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 AudioSweet ReaImGui\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Complete AudioSweet control center with ImGui interface for managing FX chains and presets.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Quick Start\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Help \u8594 ? User Manual: Full documentation with workflows and tips\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Help \u8594 ? About: Reference and credits\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Reference\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Inspired by AudioSuite-like Script by Tim Chimes 'AudioSweet' is a name originally given by Tim Chimes. This project continues to use the name in reference to his original work.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Original: Renders selected plugin to selected media item Written for REAPER 5.1 with Lua v1.1 12/22/2015 - Added PreventUIRefresh http://timchimes.com/scripting-with-reaper-audiosuite/\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Development\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script was developed with the assistance of AI tools including ChatGPT and Claude AI.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Future Development\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Planned features and experimental ideas for future implementation:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Approved for Implementation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Independent AudioSweet Run Scripts}: Create standalone action list scripts \u8226 ? Run (Stop mode): Standard execution reading all GUI ExtState settings \u8226 ? Run (Preview mode): Process items in item/time selection during preview\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Stop preview, preserve FX state/bypass\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Execute RGWH Core print/render with current FX configuration\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Return processed items to original track positions\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Resume preview workflow\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Independent Solo Script}: Unified solo logic extractable to action list \u8226 ? Priority: Focused FX/chain track \u8594 ? Default chain track \u8226 ? Can be assigned to keyboard shortcuts independently\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Right Handle Only Mode}: Extends existing audio content (different from tail) \u8226 ? Processes additional duration on right side only \u8226 ? Handle extends content that already exists in source\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Fixed-Length Tail Mode}: FX tail from non-handle content processing \u8226 ? Important: RIGHT HANDLE \u8800 ? TAIL MODE \u8226 ? Tail = reverb/delay tail printed from non-handle processed content \u8226 ? Fixed parameter: user-defined length (e.g., 3s, 5s) \u8226 ? Tail processes decay/reverb after main content, not extended source\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Deferred Ideas for Research\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Live FX Switching During Preview}: Dynamic FX parameter changes \u8226 ? Challenge: Requires real-time FX state synchronization \u8226 ? Needs investigation of REAPER API capabilities\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab {\b Auto Tail Detection}: Intelligent tail length via audio analysis \u8226 ? Analyze processed audio amplitude/RMS to detect natural decay \u8226 ? Auto-determine tail length based on reverb/delay characteristics \u8226 ? Advanced feature requiring signal processing research\sa180\par}
}

