\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Copy items and envelope points only (never tracks). When there is no Razor Selection but items are selected, move the edit cursor to the earliest selected item start at the moment of copying; with Razor Selection, respect the razor time range and move edit cursor to the earliest razor start. If only envelope points are selected, do not move the edit cursor. Designed to paste on a different target track at the same timeline position.\par}
}

