{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \u55357 ?\u56481 ? This script is extensible: you can sync it with other toggle scripts (e.g., TJF, LKC). To add them: 1. Open Action List 2. Locate the script (e.g., "TJF Hover Mode Toggle") 3. Right-click \u8594 ? "Copy selected action command ID" 4. Paste it into the USER CONFIG: Sync with other toggle scripts table below.\par}
