{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Pre-confirm dialog: shows total folders/files, lets you choose a channel naming pattern or a custom mask, then offers [Import] / [Cancel].\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Sequence only (append at the end of the target track).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Every directory that contains audio becomes a folder parent track (including the selected root).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Non\u8211-channel-split files (no ".A" or "_" match) go onto the PARENT folder track (one track per folder, including root).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Channel-split files \u8594 ? child tracks named "Ch XX" (XX is the parsed channel number).\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Recursively scans all subfolders but does NOT nest folder tracks beyond two levels: each directory with files is its own parent+children block.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab Streaming import with a small ReaImGui "Stop" window (ESC also works on some systems). On completion/abort: auto-close progress, then show a finish summary.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab No ImGui Destroy/Detach calls (avoids crashes on some builds).\sa180\sa180\par}
