{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Scan all non-hidden tracks and detect mixed item channel counts (1/2/3+). If confirmed, split items into separate tracks per channel group: "OriginalName Mono", "OriginalName Stereo", "OriginalName N-Ch" (N>=3). The original track is duplicated to preserve FX/routing; the duplicates are cleared via API and the relevant items are moved to them. No Fixed Lanes used. Effective channel count is taken from the source; takes with I_CHANMODE set to downmix/left/right are treated as Mono.\par}
}

{\rtf1\ansi\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0 \fswiss Helvetica;}{\f1 \fmodern Courier;}}
