{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Pro Tools-style "Link Track and Edit Selection". Edit Selection = Razor Area or Item Selection.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Perf principles: \u8226 ? Gate heavy scans by GetProjectStateChangeCount(). \u8226 ? Enumerate ONLY selected tracks/items when possible. \u8226 ? Cache per-track Razor; recompute on project-state changes only. \u8226 ? Apply changes only on delta tracks; publish ExtState only on change. \u8226 ? Keep Latched Virtual Range; avoid shrinking on track toggles.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Priority:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1)\tx360\tab Razor exists \u8594 ? use Razor (highest)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2)\tx360\tab Else Item Selection \u8594 ? use VIRTUAL (latched) span [min..max]\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 3)\tx360\tab Else no active range\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Notes: \u8226 ? ABCD switches added (USER OPTIONS) to enable/disable each main section: A) Razor changed \u8594 ? Track selection follows "tracks with Razor" B) Items changed (no Razor) \u8594 ? Track selection follows items' tracks C) Track selection changed + REAL TS \u8594 ? build/clear Razor + sync items (Overlap) D) Razor/Track changed \u8594 ? sync items under ACTIVE range on changed tracks \u8226 ? DEBUG_PRINT will log which section fired (A/B/C/D) for instant diagnosis.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Credits: This script was generated using ChatGPT based on design concepts and iterative testing by hsuanice. hsuanice served as the workflow designer, tester, and integrator for this tool.\par}
}

